Tuan, ada beting di setiap sisi.

3
00:01:20,450 --> 00:01:21,910
Pasir atau karang, entah.

4
00:01:24,450 --> 00:01:27,670
Kapten, para bajak laut
menyudutkan kita.

5
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:29,290
Kita harus menyerah.

6
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:35,630
Menyerahkan kapal ayahku
tak menjamin keselamatan, Tn. Phelps.

7
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:45,600
Perairan dangkal.

8
00:01:45,770 --> 00:01:47,770
Maju, buka semua layar!

9
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,610
Kapten! Kapal akan karam.

10
00:01:50,770 --> 00:01:52,190
Ini mustahil!

11
00:01:52,860 --> 00:01:55,360
Kau tahu pendapatku
soal kata itu, Tn. Phelps.

12
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,700
Buka semua layar!

13
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:02,030
Buka semua layar!

14
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,830
Buka semua layar!

15
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:10,120
Belok kiri, Harper!

16
00:02:10,540 --> 00:02:13,790
Kapal akan miring jika berbelok
dengan layar penuh.

17
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,630
Persis!

18
00:02:20,220 --> 00:02:22,010
Turunkan layarnya!

19
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,010
Cepatlah!

20
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:31,730
Pegangan, semuanya!

21
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:39,400
Terlalu dangkal.

22
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:42,530
Semua layar harus terbuka!

23
00:02:44,830 --> 00:02:47,660
-Will! Pegangan!
-Tolong!

24
00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:13,100
Kapalnya miring.

25
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,780
Pegangan!

26
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:26,030
Pegangan!

27
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,150
Kau berhasil, Kapten!

28
00:04:09,450 --> 00:04:13,790
Untuk melakukan yang mustahil
kita harus percaya itu tidak mustahil.

29
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:17,460
Tentukan arah ke London, Harper.

30
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:20,630
Tugas kita sudah selesai.

31
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:24,050
Ayo minum-minum!
Kita akan pulang!

32
00:04:45,070 --> 00:04:51,080
SELURUH DUNIA
CHARLES KINGSLEIGH

33
00:05:12,470 --> 00:05:14,140
Kapten berlabuh.

34
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,640
Kapten.

35
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:26,320
Ibu.

36
00:05:27,450 --> 00:05:28,870
Kau sudah sampai.

37
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:30,070
Akhirnya.

38
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,530
Nona Kingsleigh?

39
00:05:32,660 --> 00:05:34,750
Sudah setahun
kau dan Wonder ditunggu.

40
00:05:34,910 --> 00:05:36,160
Ada masalah.

41
00:05:36,330 --> 00:05:37,500
Bajak laut dan lainnya.

42
00:05:37,670 --> 00:05:38,920
Buku kas di kabinku.

43
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:42,250
Beri tahu Tuan Ascot
aku ingin segera menemuinya.

44
00:05:43,130 --> 00:05:46,130
Tuan Ascot wafat
ketika kau di laut.

45
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:48,090
Dia diteruskan oleh putranya.

46
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:50,140
-Hamish?
-Benar.

47
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:51,850
Kini dia ketua dewan.

48
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:54,810
Sayang sekali.

49
00:06:07,650 --> 00:06:09,700
Kau jarang mengirim surat.

50
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:12,330
Ibu tak tahu kau di mana
selama ini.

51
00:06:12,490 --> 00:06:14,160
Tiongkok mengagumkan, Ibu.

52
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:16,620
Kami menelusuri Yangtze
jauh ke pedalaman.

53
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:20,460
Banyak yang belum pernah lihat
orang berambut pirang.

54
00:06:20,630 --> 00:06:22,460
-Kau tak pernah takut?
-Tentu.

55
00:06:23,790 --> 00:06:25,630
Saat takut, kupikirkan Ayah.

56
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:28,010
Bicaramu seperti dia.

57
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,800
Aku rindu Ayah.

58
00:06:33,010 --> 00:06:34,510
Ibu juga.

59
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:37,310
Waktu berjalan cepat bagi Ibu.

60
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:40,480
Waktu memang kejam.

61
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:44,480
Waktu adalah pencuri.
Dan penjahat.

62
00:06:44,650 --> 00:06:47,900
Keluarga Ascot merayakan
kenaikan Hamish malam ini.

63
00:06:47,990 --> 00:06:48,990
Bagus.

64
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:50,490
Kita harus datang.

65
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:53,320
Undangannya hilang
dalam pengiriman.

66
00:06:53,490 --> 00:06:56,160
Tak apa. Ny. Ascot bilang
kita selalu disambut.

67
00:06:57,660 --> 00:06:59,160
Aku ada tawaran
untuk Hamish.

68
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:01,710
Hamish menikah tahun lalu, Alice.

69
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:04,000
Dia sudah melupakan penolakanmu.

70
00:07:04,170 --> 00:07:05,500
Tawaran bisnis, Ibu.

71
00:07:06,670 --> 00:07:07,920
Kau mau pergi lagi?

72
00:07:08,090 --> 00:07:09,340
Begitu cepat?

73
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:14,640
Ada hal-hal di sini
yang membutuhkan perhatianmu.

74
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,310
Usai pelayaran berikut...

75
00:07:16,470 --> 00:07:18,520
Ibu tak perlu mencemaskan
apa pun lagi.

76
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:21,190
Boleh Ibu mencemaskan
soal malam ini?

77
00:07:32,410 --> 00:07:34,370
Mestinya kau pakai gaun kuning itu.

78
00:07:34,530 --> 00:07:37,410
Jika bagus bagi
Janda Permaisuri Tiongkok...

79
00:07:37,580 --> 00:07:39,250
maka bagus bagi keluarga Ascot.

80
00:07:39,410 --> 00:07:41,540
Kau harus selalu
keras kepala?

81
00:07:41,710 --> 00:07:43,670
Tidak. Tapi itu lebih menyenangkan.

82
00:07:53,930 --> 00:07:55,050
Pakaian apa itu?

83
00:07:55,220 --> 00:07:56,600
Itu putri Kingsleigh.

84
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,760
Permisi.

85
00:07:57,930 --> 00:07:58,930
Keterlaluan.

86
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,270
Artis sirkus.

87
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,730
Nona Kingsleigh?

88
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,900
Sedang apa di sini?

89
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:08,070
Aku mau melapor
kepada Tuan Ascot.

90
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,780
Baik.

91
00:08:10,940 --> 00:08:12,400
Ikuti aku.

92
00:08:21,660 --> 00:08:22,710
Helen.

93
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:24,580
Sebuah kejutan.

94
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:27,590
Alice. Selamat datang.

95
00:08:28,090 --> 00:08:30,590
Kami cemas kau tak kembali
dengan kapal kami.

96
00:08:31,090 --> 00:08:32,970
Kapalku. Halo, Hamish.

97
00:08:33,130 --> 00:08:35,260
Tolong panggil suamiku Tuan Ascot.

98
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:38,260
Untuk itulah kami berpesta.

99
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:42,640
Nona Kingsleigh,
ini istriku, Alexandra.

100
00:08:42,810 --> 00:08:44,440
Nyonya Ascot yang baru.

101
00:08:46,310 --> 00:08:48,770
Kata Hamish kau menjelajah dunia
3 tahun ini.

102
00:08:48,940 --> 00:08:50,440
Ya. Aku baru kembali.

103
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,320
Bagaimana?

104
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:53,610
Dunia?

105
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:54,950
Ya.

106
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:59,910
Sangat menyenangkan.
Kapan-kapan kau perlu ke sana.

107
00:09:03,290 --> 00:09:04,960
Maaf mengganggu, Tn. Ascot...

108
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,620
tapi aku ingin melapor.

109
00:09:07,460 --> 00:09:08,460
Baik.

110
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,130
Ikuti aku, Nona Kingsleigh.

111
00:09:13,130 --> 00:09:14,800
Kau juga, Tn. Harcourt.

112
00:09:19,930 --> 00:09:22,430
Tuan-tuan, perkenalkan
Nn. Alice Kingsleigh.

113
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,270
Nona Kingsleigh, para dewan.

114
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,400
Selamat malam.

115
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:30,480
Dunia terbuka bagi kita,
tapi kita harus gerak cepat.

116
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:34,400
Aku yakin ekspedisi lebih jauh
di Sungai Wu...

117
00:09:34,570 --> 00:09:36,150
Maaf, Nona Kingsleigh.

118
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:38,740
Tidak ada ekspedisi lagi.

119
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,160
Apa?

120
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:44,580
Ada lowongan
di kantor administrasi kami.

121
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,660
Kau mulai dari mengurus berkas...

122
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,830
tapi nantinya...

123
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,840
Ini bukan karena Tiongkok, kan?

124
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:54,170
Tapi karena menolak lamaranmu.

125
00:09:57,340 --> 00:10:00,010
Maaf, Nn. Kingsleigh,
hanya ini yang bisa kami bantu.

126
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:04,520
Perusahaan lain takkan mau
menerima pegawai perempuan.

127
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,930
Apalagi jadi kapten kapal.

128
00:10:12,110 --> 00:10:13,440
Kau tak bisa begini.

129
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:15,690
10 persen perusahaan ini milikku.

130
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:17,700
Itu pemberian ayahmu.

131
00:10:18,450 --> 00:10:19,530
Koreksi.

132
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:21,450
Dia berikan itu ke ibumu...

133
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:24,660
yang menjualnya kepadaku
setahun lalu saat kau pergi.

134
00:10:24,830 --> 00:10:26,500
Termasuk obligasi rumah.

135
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:28,120
Rumahnya?

136
00:10:28,290 --> 00:10:30,370
Kapalmu akan menebus obligasinya.

137
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:33,670
Tapi itu kapal ayahku.

138
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:35,210
Benar.

139
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:39,220
Serahkan kapalmu...

140
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:41,470
dan rumahnya kembali.

141
00:10:41,890 --> 00:10:43,010
Mulai kerja Senin pagi...

142
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:45,310
kau akan dapat gaji
dan uang pensiun.

143
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:47,890
Dan menyerahkan Wonder?

144
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:51,230
Atau kami tak dapat menolongmu.

145
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:53,520
Atau ibumu.

146
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:06,620
Alice.

147
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,370
Alice.

148
00:11:09,580 --> 00:11:10,580
Alice!

149
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:12,170
Kenapa saham kita dijual?

150
00:11:12,920 --> 00:11:15,040
Semua Ibu lakukan untukmu, Alice.

151
00:11:15,210 --> 00:11:16,590
Agar hidupmu lebih baik.

152
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:19,170
Lima menit lalu aku kapten kapal.

153
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:21,050
Itu bukan pekerjaan bagi wanita.

154
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:24,510
Kau kehabisan waktu,
dan kau menyia-nyiakannya.

155
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:31,100
Dulu aku yakin dapat melakukan
enam hal mustahil sebelum sarapan.

156
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:34,110
Itu impian anak kecil, Alice.

157
00:11:35,730 --> 00:11:37,570
Wonder hanya sebuah kapal.

158
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:40,110
Bukan kapal biasa.

159
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,610
Itu kapal Ayah.

160
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,780
Ayah sangat mencintainya.

161
00:11:43,950 --> 00:11:45,410
Aku sangat mencintainya.

162
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:46,950
Ayah takkan biarkan ini terjadi.

163
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,540
Dia sudah tiada!

164
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:54,130
Kau tak bisa berbuat semaumu.

165
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:57,800
Setiap wanita harus
menghadapi itu, Alice.

166
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,210
Ibu juga.

167
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,550
Aku tidak mau berakhir
seperti Ibu.

168
00:12:18,570 --> 00:12:20,440
Menyerahkan Wonder?

169
00:12:21,490 --> 00:12:23,820
Meninggalkan hal yang mustahil?

170
00:12:23,990 --> 00:12:25,950
Lalu aku jadi apa?

171
00:12:28,490 --> 00:12:31,950
Jadi Alice, tentunya.

172
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:36,000
Absolem?

173
00:12:42,170 --> 00:12:43,170
Absolem.

174
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:57,100
Dia berbulan-bulan di sungai.

175
00:12:57,270 --> 00:12:59,610
Pakaiannya seperti pribumi.

176
00:12:59,770 --> 00:13:03,360
Itu bisa mengganggu pikiran lelaki,
apalagi wanita.

177
00:13:03,530 --> 00:13:05,700
-Tunggu!
-Seperti ayahnya.

178
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:08,820
Dia orang yang hebat,
tapi tidak waras.

179
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:11,490
Anaknya tak jauh berbeda.

180
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,560
Absolem.

181
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,420
Aneh.

182
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:01,540
Dikunci!
Ada orang di dalam.

183
00:14:01,710 --> 00:14:03,050
-Siapa di dalam?
-Siapa di dalam?

184
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:05,260
Kau melanggar!
Ini ruang terlarang!

185
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,720
Ambil kuncinya!

186
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:12,600
Tuan Ascot, ada orang
di ruang belajar ayahmu.

187
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:35,450
Benar-benar semakin aneh.

188
00:15:06,070 --> 00:15:07,990
Tidak, jangan lagi!

189
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:19,960
Semua kudaku. Semua pasukan.
Selamatkan dia!

190
00:15:24,750 --> 00:15:26,340
Kumpulkan semua potongan.

191
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:27,800
Tumpuklah, di sini.

192
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,680
Bagaimana keadaanku? Katakan.
Aku bisa terima.

193
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,430
Tidak terlalu hancur.

194
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:34,180
Dia hanya sebuah cangkang.

195
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,850
Hentikan. Lelucon itu-itu lagi.

196
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:38,180
Maksudmu "kuning telur"?

197
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:39,430
Aku punya lelucon baru.

198
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:40,850
Aku akan berterima kasih...

199
00:15:41,020 --> 00:15:42,020
Maaf.

200
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:44,980
Selalu ceroboh dan pandir.

201
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,980
Kupikir kau takkan menebaknya.

202
00:15:47,020 --> 00:15:48,070
Absolem.

203
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:49,780
Permisi, nona. Kami butuh itu.

204
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:51,530
Kalian membuatku jijik.

205
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:54,450
Kau sudah pergi
terlalu lama, Alice.

206
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:57,540
Dan dia akan segera pergi.

207
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:58,700
Siapa?

208
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:00,160
Apa yang terjadi?

209
00:16:00,330 --> 00:16:03,880
Semua akan jelas pada waktunya.

210
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:06,710
Untuk sekarang, bergegaslah.

211
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:11,050
Perhatikan langkahmu.

212
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,570
Hei!

213
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:45,750
-Alice.
-Oh, Alice.

214
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:48,500
Syukurlah akhirnya kau datang.

215
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:50,340
Gadis itu lagi.

216
00:16:51,590 --> 00:16:52,590
Alice.

217
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:53,760
Kau kembali.

218
00:16:58,890 --> 00:17:01,100
Jangan ramah kepadanya.
Dia terlambat.

219
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,770
Waktu kedatanganku salah?

220
00:17:02,930 --> 00:17:03,940
Sebaliknya.

221
00:17:04,100 --> 00:17:05,850
Kami takut kau tak datang.

222
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:07,230
Ada masalah apa?

223
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,770
Hatter masalahnya.

224
00:17:08,940 --> 00:17:10,610
Atau masalah Hatter.

225
00:17:10,780 --> 00:17:12,570
-Yang pertama.
-Bukan, yang kedua.

226
00:17:13,070 --> 00:17:14,070
Tweedles?

227
00:17:17,030 --> 00:17:18,030
Dia gila.

228
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,240
Hatter?

229
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:22,290
Ya, aku tahu.

230
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:23,960
Itu kelebihannya.

231
00:17:24,120 --> 00:17:25,120
Itu yang membuatnya...

232
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:27,540
dia.

233
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:28,710
Dia jadi muram...

234
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:29,920
bukan gila.

235
00:17:30,090 --> 00:17:31,550
Dia tidak tertawa.

236
00:17:32,210 --> 00:17:35,880
Kami tak dapat
membuatnya tersenyum.

237
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:40,470
Kami berharap kau bisa
bantu kami menolongnya.

238
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:42,140
Apa yang terjadi?

239
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:44,560
Ada badai yang kuat.

240
00:17:45,060 --> 00:17:49,230
Kami pergi ke Hutan Tulgey
untuk menyelidikinya.

241
00:17:53,150 --> 00:17:54,280
Ayo, kaki empat.

242
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:56,740
Tangkap!

243
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:59,160
Giliranmu!

244
00:18:02,740 --> 00:18:03,830
Ayo tangkap.

245
00:18:04,410 --> 00:18:06,660
Hatter bersikap seperti biasanya.

246
00:18:07,330 --> 00:18:08,750
Sampai...

247
00:18:10,460 --> 00:18:12,340
topi kertas biru itu...

248
00:18:13,090 --> 00:18:15,260
membuatnya teringat...

249
00:18:16,170 --> 00:18:17,340
tragedi keluarganya.

250
00:18:22,180 --> 00:18:26,810
Dibunuh oleh Jabberwocky,
pada Hari Horunvendush...

251
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:28,600
bertahun-tahun lalu.

252
00:18:29,270 --> 00:18:31,110
Lalu dia berubah.

253
00:18:33,650 --> 00:18:38,030
Hatter pasti kembali seperti dulu
jika dia melihatmu.

254
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,860
-Oh, ya.
-Benar.

255
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:42,950
Di mana dia?

256
00:18:59,590 --> 00:19:00,800
Pergilah!

257
00:19:01,090 --> 00:19:02,430
Tak boleh masuk!

258
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:04,140
Hatter, ini aku.

259
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:06,020
Alice.

260
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:10,560
Alice.

261
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:12,520
Ternyata kau.

262
00:19:12,690 --> 00:19:14,610
Kau di sini.

263
00:19:18,780 --> 00:19:20,660
Ini benar kau, bukan?

264
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:23,530
Ya, Hatter.

265
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:26,450
Bagus.

266
00:19:28,410 --> 00:19:29,960
Kau satu-satunya.

267
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,920
Kau adalah Alice.

268
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:41,010
Karena itu aku tahu
kau akan percaya aku.

269
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:42,800
Aku merindukanmu, Hatter.

270
00:19:43,970 --> 00:19:46,100
Ini soal keluargaku, Alice.

271
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:48,720
Keluargamu?

272
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:50,690
Ya.

273
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:52,270
Keluargaku.

274
00:19:52,690 --> 00:19:54,980
Meninggal bertahun-tahun lalu.

275
00:19:57,070 --> 00:19:58,900
Kupikir begitu.

276
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:00,820
Lihat.

277
00:20:01,990 --> 00:20:03,110
Kutemukan ini.

278
00:20:04,570 --> 00:20:06,330
Topi pertama yang kubuat.

279
00:20:07,080 --> 00:20:10,120
Sudah lama kubuang.

280
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:13,580
Mustahil bisa ada di sini, tapi...

281
00:20:15,210 --> 00:20:16,630
ada di sini.

282
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:19,960
Jika topi ini selamat...

283
00:20:20,130 --> 00:20:22,840
keluargaku pasti juga selamat.

284
00:20:23,630 --> 00:20:25,090
Tapi, Hatter, itu...

285
00:20:25,260 --> 00:20:28,640
Kupikir aku tak pantas
menyandang nama Hightopp.

286
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:33,520
Ayahku orang yang serius.

287
00:20:34,850 --> 00:20:36,690
Kami bertengkar hebat.

288
00:20:38,230 --> 00:20:41,650
Aku tak pernah minta maaf
saat ada kesempatan.

289
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,280
Tapi ini berarti...

290
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:49,160
aku bisa perbaiki kesalahanku.

291
00:20:49,450 --> 00:20:50,750
Hatter...

292
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:53,540
keluargamu...

293
00:20:55,210 --> 00:20:56,290
Kau...

294
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:59,500
percaya aku, kan?

295
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:02,550
Aku ingin percaya.

296
00:21:06,260 --> 00:21:07,260
Hatter!

297
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,310
Kau sedang sakit.

298
00:21:09,470 --> 00:21:11,060
Apa yang bisa kubantu?

299
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:14,640
Tentu.

300
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:18,110
Kau...

301
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:21,030
dapat mengembalikan keluargaku.

302
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:23,570
Tapi...

303
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:26,450
Hatter, persoalannya...

304
00:21:27,570 --> 00:21:29,280
keluargamu tewas.

305
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:31,990
Dulu sekali.

306
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:34,620
Kau sendiri yang bilang.

307
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:39,290
Tak ada yang dapat
mengembalikan mereka.

308
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:44,800
Kecuali kau.

309
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,180
Maaf.

310
00:21:52,430 --> 00:21:53,640
Tapi itu...

311
00:21:56,770 --> 00:21:58,520
Itu mustahil.

312
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:10,120
Kau...

313
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:12,330
bukan Alice.

314
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:18,580
Hatter, kumohon.

315
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:20,170
Keluar.

316
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:24,090
Aku tidak mengenalmu.

317
00:22:26,260 --> 00:22:27,800
Kau bukan Alice.

318
00:22:29,340 --> 00:22:31,600
Alice tentu akan percaya.

319
00:22:38,770 --> 00:22:39,770
Hatter!

320
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:43,270
Hatter, kumohon!

321
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:45,280
Kumohon!

322
00:22:53,330 --> 00:22:54,540
Kita harus berbuat sesuatu.

323
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:56,700
Dia sangat sakit.

324
00:22:57,620 --> 00:22:59,290
Aku takut dia...

325
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:00,540
sekarat.

326
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:01,960
Ya ampun.

327
00:23:02,290 --> 00:23:03,290
Ya ampun.

328
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:04,550
Tidak...

329
00:23:04,630 --> 00:23:06,800
Kita tak bisa biarkan dia mati, Alice.

330
00:23:07,800 --> 00:23:10,260
Agar dia pulih, aku harus
kembalikan keluarganya.

331
00:23:11,890 --> 00:23:12,970
Tapi itu...

332
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,890
tidak mungkin.

333
00:23:16,390 --> 00:23:18,230
Kecuali memang bisa.

334
00:23:18,390 --> 00:23:19,730
Apa?

335
00:23:24,570 --> 00:23:26,480
Kecuali ada cara.

336
00:23:26,980 --> 00:23:29,070
Tidak. Tidak boleh.

337
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:30,240
Bagaimana caranya?

338
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:33,070
Ini berbahaya.
Permintaan yang terlalu berat!

339
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,620
Bagaimana caranya?

340
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:36,330
Alice.

341
00:23:37,450 --> 00:23:39,660
Kau harus kembali
ke masa lalu.

342
00:23:40,540 --> 00:23:41,620
Gawat.

343
00:23:41,670 --> 00:23:44,250
Kembali ke masa lalu
dan selamatkan keluarga Hatter.

344
00:23:44,420 --> 00:23:46,840
Jika khayalan Hatter terwujud...

345
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:49,470
maka dia akan pulih.

346
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:51,680
Kembali ke masa lalu?

347
00:23:52,010 --> 00:23:53,050
Caranya?

348
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:54,680
Chronosphere.

349
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,680
Maaf, Chrono apa?

350
00:23:56,850 --> 00:23:57,850
Chronosphere.

351
00:23:58,270 --> 00:24:01,940
Sumber tenaga
Jam Agung Semua Waktu.

352
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:06,820
Benda itu dapat membawa orang
melewati Lautan waktu.

353
00:24:07,110 --> 00:24:10,280
Kami tak dapat gunakan
karena kami sudah di masa lalu.

354
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:13,280
Jika dirimu di masa lalu melihat
dirimu dari masa depan...

355
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,160
Apa yang terjadi?

356
00:24:16,330 --> 00:24:17,700
Itu belum pernah terjadi.

357
00:24:17,870 --> 00:24:19,370
Tapi jika itu terjadi...

358
00:24:19,790 --> 00:24:22,290
semuanya akan musnah.

359
00:24:23,210 --> 00:24:24,710
Kedengarannya berbahaya.

360
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:27,000
Memang. Sangat berbahaya.

361
00:24:27,170 --> 00:24:31,220
Karena kau bukan dari sini,
hanya kau yang bisa gunakan.

362
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:32,720
Itu tidak mustahil...

363
00:24:33,050 --> 00:24:34,050
hanya...

364
00:24:34,220 --> 00:24:35,800
sulit dilakukan.

365
00:24:36,390 --> 00:24:37,640
Dapat!

366
00:24:40,560 --> 00:24:42,390
Hatter teman sejatiku.

367
00:24:42,560 --> 00:24:45,400
Jika dia butuh bantuan,
aku akan menolongnya.

368
00:24:46,900 --> 00:24:47,940
Alice!

369
00:24:48,020 --> 00:24:49,860
-Berani sekali.
-Aku tahu dia pasti bantu.

370
00:24:50,480 --> 00:24:52,570
Di mana Chronosphere itu?

371
00:24:52,990 --> 00:24:54,990
Di tangan Waktu.
Itu punya dia.

372
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:59,580
Maaf. Waktu seorang pria?

373
00:25:02,250 --> 00:25:06,500
Dia tinggal dalam kehampaan kekal,
di istana abadi.

374
00:25:07,250 --> 00:25:10,710
Lewat sini, 1,6 kilometer
melewati bandul.

375
00:25:20,260 --> 00:25:21,600
Dingin sekali.

376
00:25:22,020 --> 00:25:24,270
Temukan istana Waktu,
pinjam Chronosphere...

377
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:26,100
kembali ke masa lalu
pada Hari Horunvendush...

378
00:25:26,270 --> 00:25:29,730
selamatkan keluarga Hatter,
maka Hatter akan selamat.

379
00:25:29,900 --> 00:25:33,740
Usahakan tidak merusak masa lalu,
sekarang, atau masa depan.

380
00:25:34,900 --> 00:25:37,070
Aku hanya ingin menolong.

381
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:38,950
Tak mungkin ada masalah.

382
00:25:55,930 --> 00:25:57,970
Sampai jumpa, Alice.

383
00:25:58,140 --> 00:25:59,890
Hatter mengandalkanmu.

384
00:26:00,050 --> 00:26:01,890
Kami semua juga.

385
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:30,600
Halo?

386
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:34,360
Ada orang?

387
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,340
Halo?

388
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:27,990
Koridor bentuk tubuhku
yang bodoh.

389
00:28:36,130 --> 00:28:39,260
Kapan hari ini berakhir?

390
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:43,260
Baju ini melekat bagai
celana panjang berkeringat.

391
00:28:50,520 --> 00:28:53,980
KEDIAMAN PENGHUNI
BAWAH TANAH

392
00:28:57,270 --> 00:28:59,820
Siapa yang berhenti?

393
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:01,240
Siapa yang berdentang...

394
00:29:01,610 --> 00:29:02,950
untuk terakhir kalinya?

395
00:29:03,110 --> 00:29:04,110
Berdentang...

396
00:29:04,410 --> 00:29:06,660
terakhir kalinya?

397
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:20,710
Brilliam...

398
00:29:21,840 --> 00:29:23,380
Hinkle.

399
00:29:32,270 --> 00:29:34,270
Brilliam Hinkle.

400
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:37,100
Waktumu berakhir.

401
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:51,910
Biar kusimpan kau, Tn. Hinkle...

402
00:29:51,990 --> 00:29:53,040
MAKAM BAWAH TANAH

403
00:29:53,080 --> 00:29:55,830
...di tempat yang tepat,
sesuai abjad.

404
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:01,590
Higgens.

405
00:30:02,460 --> 00:30:04,260
Highbottom.

406
00:30:04,420 --> 00:30:06,090
Belum mati.

407
00:30:06,340 --> 00:30:08,340
Highturn.

408
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:10,510
Highview, Himmelby.

409
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:13,430
Hinkle.

410
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:14,890
Kuharap kau bahagia.

411
00:30:15,060 --> 00:30:17,100
Kuharap kau menggunakan
waktu dengan baik.

412
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:18,350
Selamat malam.

413
00:30:23,150 --> 00:30:24,240
Siapa itu?

414
00:30:24,690 --> 00:30:26,320
Aku melihatmu.

415
00:30:26,570 --> 00:30:28,360
Bagaimana kau bisa masuk?

416
00:30:28,610 --> 00:30:30,580
Itu mustahil.

417
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:33,490
Keluarlah, cacing kecil.

418
00:30:37,170 --> 00:30:38,830
-Ternyata seorang gadis.
-Kumohon, Tuan.

419
00:30:39,330 --> 00:30:40,540
Maaf mengganggu...

420
00:30:40,710 --> 00:30:42,040
tapi aku minta waktu sebentar.

421
00:30:42,710 --> 00:30:44,300
Waktu?

422
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:47,010
Nona muda...

423
00:30:48,340 --> 00:30:50,140
Akulah...

424
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:52,050
Waktu.

425
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,430
Yang tak terbatas...

426
00:30:55,930 --> 00:30:57,060
yang kekal...

427
00:30:58,020 --> 00:30:59,480
yang abadi...

428
00:31:01,150 --> 00:31:03,070
yang tak terukur.

429
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:06,190
Kecuali kau punya jam.

430
00:31:08,110 --> 00:31:09,490
Jadi, sebagai Waktu...

431
00:31:09,660 --> 00:31:12,030
aku harus berikan
sebagian diriku...

432
00:31:12,200 --> 00:31:14,120
agar kau memilikiku.

433
00:31:14,290 --> 00:31:16,160
Paham maksudku?

434
00:31:16,330 --> 00:31:17,370
Ya.

435
00:31:17,500 --> 00:31:18,540
Benarkah?

436
00:31:20,460 --> 00:31:21,750
Kau janji akan cepat?

437
00:31:22,250 --> 00:31:23,420
Akan kucoba...

438
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:25,460
Karena aku paling tidak suka...

439
00:31:25,630 --> 00:31:28,340
orang yang tak bisa
dan tak mau...

440
00:31:32,350 --> 00:31:35,810
tak mampu membuat
kalimat singkat.

441
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:38,020
Temanku dalam bahaya.

442
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:39,730
Cukup omong kosongnya!

443
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:43,560
Aku punya urusan penting.

444
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,480
Kumohon!

445
00:31:45,730 --> 00:31:47,570
Kau belum jawab pertanyaanku.

446
00:31:50,780 --> 00:31:51,780
Satu menit.

447
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:55,540
Kenapa kau mengantongi
prajurit yang gugur itu?

448
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:56,790
Perlihatkan dia.

449
00:31:57,790 --> 00:31:58,790
Dia rusak.

450
00:31:59,660 --> 00:32:00,670
Mati.

451
00:32:00,830 --> 00:32:02,710
Ini punya ayahku. Takkan kulepas.

452
00:32:03,420 --> 00:32:06,420
Semua orang pasti akan berpisah
dengan segalanya.

453
00:32:13,010 --> 00:32:14,010
Lihatlah.

454
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:22,770
Jam Agung Semua Waktu
yang menakjubkan.

455
00:32:26,270 --> 00:32:28,610
Dia adalah aku,
dan aku adalah dia...

456
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:32,450
dari dulu sampai selamanya.

457
00:32:33,030 --> 00:32:34,910
Aku mengarang puisi itu.

458
00:32:36,700 --> 00:32:38,910
Ingat. Semangat, semuanya.

459
00:32:39,500 --> 00:32:40,960
Wilkins!

460
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:42,540
Bahu ke belakang,
mata ke depan.

461
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:45,330
Bagaimana mesinku
yang tak terkalahkan?

462
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:46,590
-Itu...
-Diam!

463
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:49,340
Hanya bicara jika diajak bicara.

464
00:32:50,340 --> 00:32:51,720
-Dia diajak bicara.
-Omong kosong!

465
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:53,180
Mesinnya, Wilkins.

466
00:32:53,340 --> 00:32:54,890
Bagaimana keadaannya?

467
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,730
Halo.

468
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,730
Siapa kau?

469
00:33:02,890 --> 00:33:06,560
Pekerja-pekerja kecil ini
ialah Detik.

470
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:07,980
Menarik!

471
00:33:08,150 --> 00:33:10,440
Setiap Detik
patut diperhitungkan.

472
00:33:10,610 --> 00:33:11,900
Menghitungnya? Mustahil.

473
00:33:13,650 --> 00:33:15,950
Mereka bodoh.

474
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:24,120
Aku kasar sekali.

475
00:33:24,290 --> 00:33:25,420
Maaf.

476
00:33:33,260 --> 00:33:35,800
Sudah kubilang. Bodoh.

477
00:33:35,970 --> 00:33:37,010
Ayo.

478
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:43,350
Pertanyaanmu.

479
00:33:43,520 --> 00:33:46,020
Apa pertanyaanmu?
Waktumu satu menit.

480
00:33:47,610 --> 00:33:48,730
Ini soal Hatter...

481
00:33:49,190 --> 00:33:51,280
Tarrant Hightopp. Teman baikku.

482
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:54,320
Dia yakin keluarganya yang tewas
masih hidup.

483
00:33:54,490 --> 00:33:56,070
Itu mustahil karena...

484
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:58,370
Jabberwocky membunuhnya
pada Hari Horunvendush...

485
00:33:58,530 --> 00:33:59,780
kubunuh Jabberwocky
pada Hari Frabjous...

486
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:00,990
dan aku mau pinjam Chronosphere.

487
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,250
Penting agar...

488
00:34:04,290 --> 00:34:05,960
Chronosphere.

489
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:07,630
Itu belum satu menit.

490
00:34:07,790 --> 00:34:09,090
Kau ingin meminjamnya.

491
00:34:09,460 --> 00:34:10,800
Meminjamnya.

492
00:34:11,460 --> 00:34:12,510
Mencurinya.

493
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:14,630
Ya.

494
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:19,800
Kau ingin...

495
00:34:21,680 --> 00:34:23,930
menghancurkan sejarah.

496
00:34:24,390 --> 00:34:26,810
Chronosphere sumber tenaga
Jam Agung.

497
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:28,150
Tapi aku membutuhkannya.

498
00:34:28,310 --> 00:34:29,690
Tanpanya, Hatter takkan pulih.

499
00:34:29,860 --> 00:34:31,650
-Dan aku harus...
-Wilkins!

500
00:34:32,020 --> 00:34:33,190
Wilkins!

501
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,360
Pintu bodoh.

502
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:36,360
Tuan memanggil?

503
00:34:36,530 --> 00:34:39,450
Wilkins, tolong usir...

504
00:34:39,620 --> 00:34:42,620
gadis berambut pirang ini.

505
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:44,120
Segera, Tuan!

506
00:34:44,290 --> 00:34:45,960
Penyusup dilarang!

507
00:34:46,120 --> 00:34:47,710
Terima kasih Waktumu, Tuan.

508
00:34:48,330 --> 00:34:49,630
Ayo cepat.

509
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:52,040
Apa?

510
00:34:52,210 --> 00:34:53,210
